name: Needle felted purple flower adjustable ring
description: This five petal flower has been needle felted from 100% wool to make a flower which has then been stitched onto a silver plated adjustable ring.  The petals are made from lavender coloured wool whereas the centre is from a mauve coloured wool.  The flower measures 1.5" across approximately with the ring fitting sizes 5-10.  This is a delicate piece of jewellery and due to it being made from wool I would not recommend it getting wet.  Beautiful and whimsical, just the thing to add interest and receive compliments for!

name: Yellow flower stud earrings
description: Five petal resin flowers in yellow fading to white with an orange centre measuring 3cm across. Studs are 1.1cm long, are silver plated and nickel free.  I love bright colours and flowers and these are the perfect combination of the two! They're cute and will brighten up any summer outfit, so go on treat yourself or someone you know who will love them!

name: Orange bird cabochon adjustable ring
description: A pretty little bird on an adjustable silver plated ring with round orange beads as the landscape.  The bird is made of resin and measures 1" wide and 1/2" from feet to top of it's head.  The ring will fit adult sizes 5-10, the ring shank is 7mm wide tapering down to 5mm and the base is 16mm wide.  This ring is a pretty sweet thing to wear as it's a bit unusual and should brighten up anyone's day!
